Ruben Fabin Pereira Mrquez (born 28 January 1968 in Montevideo) is a former Uruguayan footballer.[1] Pereira made 27 appearances for the senior Uruguay national football team from 1988 to 1996,[1] including two appearances at the 1990 FIFA World Cup finals.[2] He also played in the 1989 Copa Amrica. 
